section.home-testimonial__container.py-5
  .container
    .home-section__head.mb-4
      h2#testimonial.home-section__head-title.text-center.font-black
        | Time to make your parents REALLY proud

    .row.home-testimonial__box.mx-auto
      .col-md-4.home-testimonial__image-container.p-0
        = image_tag 'home/index/testimonial-student-family.png', class: 'img-fluid mx-auto home-testimonial__image', alt: "A student's family"
      .col-md-8.home-testimonial__text.d-flex.justify-content-center.flex-column
        p
          ' &ldquo;I was really worried when he said that he wanted to do a startup in his college.
          ' I thought college was all about grades and attendance but then I saw him
          ' code all the day in his room. He spends money for his company and not for shopping.
          ' It feels really great. He told me about his experience in Silicon Valley,
          | and he seems to have learnt a lot from that.&rdquo;
        p.font-semibold.pt-2
          ' &ndash; Subbalakshmi Rajan
          .font-regular.home-testimonial__text--author-sub
            | (Suraj Rajan&rsquo;s Mother)

